FBIS3-38653 "drweu025aa_94018" FBIS-WEU-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 February 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Finland `Sharply Condemns' Attack on Sarajevo LD0602160894 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network in Finnish 1400 GMT 6 Feb 94 LD0602160894 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network Language: Finnish Article Type:BFN [Text] Finland has sharply condemned the latest attack on the civilian population of Sarajevo. According to Foreign Minister Heikki Haavisto, an air strike against those besieging Sarajevo would be a very difficult decision for Finland. The Nordic countries have, however, discussed the possibility of stepping up armed protection of humanitarian aid transports.
